    "description": "Join the 1mg Capital India family as a Backend Developer in Gwalior. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout 1mg Capital India:\n1mg Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 1mg Capital India!",
